headline: Rollins (ROL) Q4 Earnings Match Estimates
summary: Rollins (ROL) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 0% and 1.95%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Rollins (NYSE:ROL) Exceeds Q4 Expectations
summary: Pest control company Rollins (NYSE:ROL) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q4 CY2024, with sales up 10.4% year on year to $832.2 million. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.23 per share was in line with analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Rollins: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: ATLANTA (AP) — Rollins Inc. ROL) on Wednesday reported fourth-quarter profit of $105.7 million. The Atlanta-based company said it had net income of 22 cents per share.
